## Reconciliation Finding

`data/agent_run_log.csv` row `RUN-004` says: "Supplier search in progress. 3 quotes received so far."

`data/quote_master.csv` contains only one quote for `EXP-20260630-001`:

| Quote ID | Supplier ID | Supplier | Quote received | Selected | Notes |
|---|---:|---|---|---|---|
| Q-002 | SUP-003 | Spice Valley Exports | 2026-06-28T11:00:00 | TRUE | APEDA certified. FOB Kochi. |

No additional quote rows for `EXP-20260630-001` were found in `quote_master.csv` or the case artifact manifest. The reliable current quote-proof count is therefore `1`, not `3`.

## Gate Status

