## Material Risk Flags

1. The master case had `supplier_search_done=TRUE`, but quote proof is incomplete. This was reconciled to `FALSE`.
2. The master case had candidate HSN/ITC-HS `0902.30`. That appears inconsistent with turmeric powder and should not be used externally.
