4. No buyer RFQ attachment or D&B receipt is present in the case evidence folder. The buyer-verification note is local-register evidence only.
5. IndiaMART was checked as a configured source but direct fetch returned HTTP 403 in this run, so it was not used as verified supplier evidence.

