+# Demand Signal Audit - 2026-06-30 13:50:03 IST
+
+Scope: repo-local audit only. Sources inspected: `data/master_cases.csv`, `data/source_health.csv`, `data/agent_run_log.csv`, `config/sources.gov.yaml`, `config/sources.export.yaml`, `outputs/source_scans/*`, and `outputs/demand_signals/*`.
+
+## 1. Demand signals found / validated
+
+- The demand digest reports 12 active signals: 6 EXPORT and 6 GOV, sourced from `data/master_cases.csv`. This count excludes the rejected GOV row but includes weaker historical/recovered rows. Evidence: `outputs/demand_signals/demand_signal_digest_20260630_132504.md`; `outputs/demand_signals/demand_signal_digest_20260630_132504.json`.
+- Validated fresh EXPORT opportunities: `EXP-20260630-003`, `EXP-20260630-004`, `EXP-20260630-005`, and `EXP-20260630-006` were created by the export RFQ batch scan from TradeKey and UNDP public notices. Evidence: `outputs/source_scans/export_rfq_batch_scan_20260630_131453.md`; `outputs/source_scans/export_rfq_batch_scan_20260630_131453.json`; `outputs/source_scans/export_candidate_details_20260630_130726.json`; `data/master_cases.csv`.
+- Validated fresh GOV opportunities: `GOV-20260630-003`, `GOV-20260630-004`, `GOV-20260630-005`, `GOV-20260630-006`, and `GOV-20260630-007` were created by the GOV radar scan from GeM and Maharashtra e-Tender public listings. Evidence: `outputs/source_scans/gov_radar_batch_20260630131554.md`; `outputs/source_scans/gov_radar_batch_20260630131554.json`; `data/master_cases.csv`.
+- Weak or internal-only rows: `EXP-20260630-002` is reconstructed from local registers with missing original RFQ URL and buyer identity; `EXP-20260630-001` has only generic Alibaba RFQ landing evidence and missing buyer-specific RFQ material; `GOV-20260630-001` needs a specific GeM bid number/document URL/PDF or owner screenshot before downstream reliance. Evidence: `outputs/case_reports/EXP-20260630-002/rfq_evidence_intake_EXP-20260630-002.md`; `data/agent_run_log.csv`; `outputs/case_reports/EXP-20260630-001/audit_EXP-20260630-001.md`; `data/master_cases.csv`.
+- Non-actionable rows: `GOV-20260630-002` is already rejected for deadline and past-experience kill rules; the mock GOV/EXPORT rows are fixture-only and explicitly marked "Do not treat as real". Evidence: `outputs/case_reports/GOV-20260630-002/no_go_reason_note.txt`; `outputs/source_scans/daily_morning_autopilot_mock_20260630_130941.json`.
+
