+
+## 3. Evidence quality and missing information
+
+- UNDP cases `EXP-20260630-005` and `EXP-20260630-006`: strongest source quality because the notice pages returned HTTP 200 and include RFQ process, reference numbers, publication dates, deadlines, contacts, and Quantum portal warning. Missing: full tender attachments, eligibility, delivery terms, packaging/specs, destination import conditions, registration feasibility, and supplier proof. Evidence: `outputs/source_scans/export_candidate_details_20260630_130726.json`; `outputs/source_scans/export_rfq_batch_scan_20260630_131453.md`.
+- GeM cases `GOV-20260630-003` to `GOV-20260630-006`: good radar evidence because the scan selected public bid document URLs and recorded HTTP 200 status, but none has been deep-read. Missing: EMD, buyer location, eligibility, experience, OEM/certification clauses, delivery/payment/penalty terms, and actual BOQ line items. Evidence: `outputs/source_scans/gov_radar_batch_20260630131554.json`; `data/master_cases.csv`.
+- `GOV-20260630-007`: public evidence exists, but the deadline is 2026-06-30, the product reads like sanitation manpower/service work, and the demand digest scores it negative. Missing: usable time window and deep-readed eligibility. Evidence: `data/master_cases.csv`; `outputs/demand_signals/demand_signal_digest_20260630_132504.md`.
+- TradeKey cases `EXP-20260630-003` and `EXP-20260630-004`: real public links were found, but buyer details are hidden or masked, deadlines and quantities are not recorded in the case register, and the rice lead has a duplicate-looking listing. Evidence: `outputs/source_scans/export_rfq_batch_scan_20260630_131453.md`; `outputs/source_scans/export_candidate_details_20260630_130726.json`; `data/master_cases.csv`.
+- Historical active rows `EXP-20260630-001`, `GOV-20260630-001`, and `EXP-20260630-002` should not be treated as today's best evidence-backed demand: Alibaba buyer-specific evidence is missing for `EXP-20260630-001`; exact GeM verification is missing for `GOV-20260630-001`; original buyer/RFQ evidence is missing for `EXP-20260630-002`. Evidence: `data/agent_run_log.csv`; `outputs/case_reports/EXP-20260630-001/audit_EXP-20260630-001.md`; `outputs/case_reports/EXP-20260630-002/rfq_evidence_intake_EXP-20260630-002.md`.
+
